en_902032_0	Track and field events in the 10th Defence Services Athletics Championship - 2018 (DSAC) started on Tuesday (13) at Sugathadasa Stadium, Colombo 13.
en_902032_1	During today’s events, Private H.D.V Lakshani of the Sri Lanka Army Women’s Corps by marking 13.58 meters made a new game record in the women’s Triple Jump event.
en_902032_2	The championship tournament will continue until Sunday (16) to culminate with the closing ceremony.
en_902032_3	Major General Damapath Fernando, Chief of Staff is scheduled to participate in the closing event as the Chief Guest.
